    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly option to get you from point A to point B? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has seen better days and shows significant signs of wear, both inside and out. Mechanically, it needs some attention and is best suited for a handy buyer or someone looking for a project car. If you're comfortable with a fixer-upper and want the lowest possible entry price, this could be the opportunity you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
